description:
Cloud-Native and Kubernetes and common buzz words and something most companies are wrestling with.

We're pleased to announce a panel discussion focused on "the future of cloud".

We plan to discuss all things cloud, what the future looks like, emerging tech and how to succeed on your cloud journey.

Our panelists are:

Jonathan Shanks - https://www.linkedin.com/in/jonathanshanks/

Dan Evans - https://www.linkedin.com/in/danevans/

Andrew Bold - https://www.linkedin.com/in/andybold/

If you have any particular topics you're keen to hear about please let us know!
title: Future of cloud - a panel discussion
